Njengobe bekuphrofethiwe, siphepho lesinguRosa siphelela emuva njengobe sihamba etikwemahlatsi langasenyakatfo yeLwandle laseMexico.
Nobe kunjalo, iRosa itawuletsa umonakalo lomkhulu lotawubangela tikhukhula eNyakatfo yeMexico naseNshonalanga yeMelika.
Ngesikhatsi siphepho Rosa siba siphepho lesingu-Category 1, umoya bewuhamba ngesivinini lesingaba ngemakhilomitha langu-136 ngelihora, nga-5 ekuseni ngeLisontfo leLisempumalanga ngeLisontfo, futsi besisendzaweni lengemakhilomitha langu-600 eningizimu-nshonalanga yePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
