Bantfu bayelulekwa kutsi bangangeni emahlatsini ngetinyawo nangabe babona kutsi likhula lelishisako litawubangela kutsi kube netindzawo letishisako.
Timvula letinkhulu tingabangela kutsi tibe nemvula lenkhulu, bese lesiphepho siletsa umoya lomkhulu kanye nesitunge.
