I-Wayde Sims Shooting: emaphoyisa abophe Diteon Simpson ngekuhlobana nesidvumbu sebalingisi be-LSU
Emaphoyisa asebambe umsolwa wekubulawa kwaWayde Sims, lobekalijaha leminyaka lemashumi lamabili lebelisidlalela i-LSU.
I-Dython Simpson, ineminyaka lengu-20 budzala, yaboshwa, iboshelwa licala lekubulala, ngekusho kweliphoyisa le-Baton Rouge.
I-SASAC yente li-video lelikhombisa Sims naSimpson balwa futsi batsi Sims ulahlekelwe nguletintfo takhe tekubuka ngesikhatsi balwa.
Emaphoyisa atfole letigilasi endzaweni yesehlakalo atsi atfole i-DNA ya-Simpson kuto, ngekusho kwe-WAFB, i-CBS lencenye.
Emaphoyisa atsi Simpson wavuma enkantolo kutsi nguye lowadubula Wayde wambulala.
Ngekusho kwemmeli wakhe, imali yesibambiso lebeyivele ikhona beyikungu-R350,000.
Luphiko lwelihhovisi lemtsetfo wesifundza e-East Baton Rouge, e-Boston, e-Illinois, e-U.S.A., lwashicilela umbiko wekufa lokungaba khona ngeLesihlanu, lokusho kutsi kufa kwemuntfu kubangelwe kushaywa ngesibhamu enhloko nasenhloko.
I-SAS ifuna kubonga emaphoyisa ase-Louisiana, liphoyisa le-Criminal Investigation Division, emaphoyisa ase-Southern University kanye nebantfu bakulesigodzi ngekusita kwabo ekuphenyetweni kwalobogadzi.
Joe Alleva, longusi wezemidlalo e-LSU wabonga labagadzi ngekukhutsala kwabo kanye nekucinisa kwetemtsetfo.
Sims abeneminyaka lengu-20 budzala.
Lomdlali longemamitha lamabili budze wakhulela e-Baton Rouge lapho khona babe wakhe, Wayne, naye wadlala i-baseball ku-LSU.
Ulingise 5.6 yemaphuzu, nekutsatsa 2,6 nge game ngesikhatsi semidlalo yekugcina.
Will Wade, longumceceshi we baseball e-LSU, utsi ngeLesihlanu ekuseni licembu lakhe belibukeka lilahlekelwe likhono futsi lihlase kabuhlungu ngenca yekushona kwaWayde.
"Loku yintfo umuntfu lahlala akhatsatekile ngayo", kwasho Wade.
