Eminyakeni lesiphohlongo lengiyikadze ngikulomkhandlu webaholi belicembu letisebenti, imihlangano yeLesihlanu beyingesiso lesimo.
Lokubuhlungu kutsi, loku akusiko loku lokukhulunywa ngako etinkhulumiswaneni letinyenti lamuhla, futsi setsembiso semibuso lencono naletfobekile siye sashiyelwa ngephandle, nangabe-ke sake sacala.
Kuye kwacaca kutsi imibono leyehlukene ayihambisani naloko lokushiwo licembu letisebenti, futsi kutsi imibono leyehlukene icatjangwa ngekuvumelana naloko lokushiwo baholi belicembu.
Loku kwacala masinyane ngemuva kwekuba Jeremy abeyindvuna, ngesikhatsi labanye lebengisebenta nabo lebengicabanga kutsi banemibono lefanako ngetepolitiki, bacala kungilindzela kutsi ngente tintfo ngendlela lengeke ibonakale, futsi ngisekele imibono lebengingavumelani nayo, kungaba kutsi ikumicimbi yetekuphepha kwesive nobe i-EU Common Market.
Ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi nangikhuluma emphakatsini - futsi loko akubaluleki - kuphuma luhambo lwekungihlambalata kumakheli etinkhundla tekuchumana, lokufaka ekhatsi kungidvonsela phansi, kungiphika kutsi ngingumholi, kanye nekungicosha ecenjini Letisebenti.
Akusimi ngedvwa lonelwati lolunjalo.
Ngiyati kutsi ngiphumelele kunebantfu lengisebenta nabo, ngobe imibono lenginayo ngekwabo ivame kuhlobana netindzaba tepolitiki.
Ngiyitsandza kakhulu indlela bantfu labenta ngayo tintfo ngendlela lefanele, futsi bayayihlonipha indlela labanye bantfu labenta ngayo, ikakhulukati labo lababhekene nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi nobe kuhlushwa ngebuhlanga onkhe emalanga kodvwa bangaphelelwa ngemandla.
Lokunye lokwenta bantfu badvumateke esikhatsini setfu lesengcile, yindlela bantfu labahlaselwa ngayo ngalokuphelele.
Jeremy Corbyn, kuleliviki lelengcile, watsi licembu lebasebenti kumele liyekele emasiko lalahlekako.
Liciniso likutsi asisilo nje liSontfo lelicinile. Nobe ngabe yini lesiyentako, nobe kushintja kwetimiso, kuyaceka.
Ngitfole seluleko lesinyenti kuleminyaka lemibili lendlulile sekutsi ngente lokuncane, ngingasebentisi kakhulu futsi ngente kahle.
Kodvwa ngakhetsa kungatingeneli tindzaba tepolitiki kuze ngikwente loko.
Kusukela ngicala kuba lilunga lelicembu letisebenti ngisesengumfundzi eminyakeni lengu 32 leyendlulile, ngikhutsatwe kunganaki kwahulumende waThatcher lokwashiya likamelo lami lekufundza lihlehla, ngisebente ngekutimisela kute ngente imisebenti leminyenti emphakatsini, kulabo labayidzinga kakhulu, ngisho nobe bengisesigungwini selidolobha nobe ngisephalamende.
Angizange sengicabange kutsi ngingakhona kwenta lomsebenti.
Kute umuntfu eNottingham East longaba nekungabata ngetinchubomgomo tami kanye nekungavumelani kwami nebaholi balomuhla.
Kulabo labangazange bavumelane nalomtsetfosivivinywa ngaLesihlanu, ngitsandza nje kusho kutsi njengobe lelive selibangise eBrexit, letawulimata emakhaya etfu, emabhizinisini kanye nasetinsitweni temphakatsi, angiyiboni intsandvo yekucitsa sikhatsi sami nemandla ekubambeni buholi belicembu letisebenti.
Kepha umlayeto wami munye, lengifuna kuwendlulisela, awukabuki ku Nottingham Momentum, kepha kulabo lengibakhetselako, nobe bangemalunga elicembu lebasebenti nobe cha: Nginiphatsa ngekutigcabha futsi ngetsembisa kutsi kute kusongela ngekuhlubuka nobe kungetsembeki kutangivimba kutsi ngente loko lengikubona kukuhle kini nonkhe.
