John Edward: Emakhono elulwimi ayintfo ledzingekako kumuntfu lohlala emhlabeni wonkhe
Tikolwa tangasese eScotland tatiwa ngekuphumelela kwebafundzi bato, futsi loku kuchubeke nga-2018 ngetindlela letinsha, letihle tekuhlola, letichutjekiswe ngekutfutfukiswa kwemfundvo leyehlukene kanye nekuhlanganyela emidlalweni, emicimbini, umculo kanye naletinye tintfo letiphatselene nemphakatsi.
Kulelive, tikolwa letibalelwa ku-30 000 tilawulwa yi-Scottish Council of Independent Schools (i-SCIS), futsi tifuna kuniketa bafundzi kanye nebatali babo lusito lolusezingeni lelisetulu.
Tikolwa leticeceshelwe tifundvo letiphakeme tihlose kucecesha bafundzi kute bakhone kutfola imfundvo lephakeme, kutfola umsebenti, kanye nekulungela kuba sakhamuti selive.
Njengobe singothishela lowenta luhlelo loluhleleke kahle lwekuhlola, siyabona kutsi lulwimi lwetinyoni luyachubeka nekuba yincenye lebalulekile etikolweni.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, uyakuva".
Nangabe ukhuluma nayo ngelulwimi lwayo, ingcondvo yayo iyavakala.
Loku kusikhumbuta kutsi singeke setsembele esiNgisini kuphela ekwakheni budlelwane nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Imiphumela yeluhlolo lwalemnyaka ikhombisa kutsi tilwimi tihamba embili eluhlwini lwetikolo letiphakeme letibhaliswe ngemphumelelo etikolweni leticeceshiwe.
Emaphesenti langu-68 ebantfwana lafundza lulwimi lolwengetiwe batfola i-A.
Loluhlolo lolwentiwa etikolweni letingu-74 ku-SCIS, lwaveta kutsi bafundzi labangu-72 ekhulwini batfole ticu te-A esifundvweni se-Mandarin, kantsi labangu-72 ekhulwini batfole ticu te-A esifundvweni se-German, labangu-69 ekhulwini batfola ticu te-A esifundvweni se-French, kantsi labangu-63 ekhulwini batfola ticu te-A esifundvweni se-Spanish.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolo letiyimfihlo eScotland tisekela kufundza tilwimi letinsha njengelikhono lelibalulekile lelitawudzingeka kubantfwana kanye nalabasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Nyalo, lulwimi, njengentfo lotikhetsela yona, lufakwa etulu njengetifundvo tesayensi (isayensi, bucwepheshe, bungcweti, nemathematics) etikolweni tangasese nakuletinye tifundvo.
Luhlolo lwanga-2014 lolwentiwa yi-UK Commission for Employment and Skills, lukhomba kutsi tizatfu letibantfu labacashiwe labacabanga kutsi kubumatima kutfola umsebenti, ngu 17% ngenca yekushoda kwebantfu labacashiwe labanelwati lolungetiwe lwetilwimi.
Kungako-ke, lwati lwetilwimi luya ngekuba lubalulekile ekucecesheni bantfu labasha kutsi bakhone kwenta imisebenti yabo esikhatsini lesitako.
Njengobe imisebenti leminyenti nyalo idzinga lwati lwetilwimi, kufanele ube nalo lelive leligcwele bantfu labanyenti.
Kunobe ngumuphi umsebenti bantfu labangawenta, kufundza lolunye lulwimi kutawuba lusito lolukhulu esikhatsini lesitako.
Kufinyelela bantfu labasuka kulamanye emave ngalokusuka enhlitiyweni kutawuniketa umuntfu lonetintfo letinyenti ematfuba ekutsi abe ncono kunalabanye.
Ngekusho kweluhlolo lwe-YouGov lwanga-2013 lolwentiwa kulabangetulu kwa-4000 bantfu baseNgilandi labadzala, emaphesenti langu-75 abo abengakhoni kukhuluma lolunye lulwimi ngalokwanele kute bacoce kahle, kantsi siFulentji kwakunguleso kuphela lesasikhulunywa linani lelingu- 2 ngelinani lelingu- 1 ngelinani, lokusho emaphesenti langu-15.
Kungako kubalulekile kutsi bantfwana bafundze tilwimi letinsha kusukela ebuntfwaneni.
Kubala, ikakhulukati emaveni lasatfutfuka, kutawuniketa bantfwana litfuba lelihle lekutfola umsebenti lonetintfo letibalulekile.
Kulesinye sifundza, tifundvo tentiwa ngetilwimi letehlukene.
Letinye tikolwa titawugcila kakhulu etikwetilwimi tendzabuko, kantsi letinye titawufundzisa tilwimi letibonakala tibalulekile eUK letibheke ku-2020, njengesiMandarin nobe siJapane.
Ngisho nobe ngabe umntfwana wakho unelutsandvo lwati lolunjani, utawuhlale akhona kukhetsa lulwimi lafuna kulusebentisa etikolweni leticeceshiwe letinebantfu labaceceshiwe.
Tikolo taseScotland letitimele tiyatinikela kuniketa imfundvo lesisekelo lesitawenta bantfwana bakulungele futsi ibafundzise ngemakhono latawubasita baphumelele, nobe ngabe likusasa libaphatseleni.
Akungabateki kutsi esikhatsini setfu, esimeni semhlaba jikelele semabhizinisi, tilwimi tihlala tibalulekile esikhatsini lesitako selive, futsi loko kumele kubonakale etikwemfundvo.
Ecinisweni, lulwimi lwema-Afrika kumele lubekwe njengelulwimi lolwati kukhuluma.
Tikolo letiyimfihlo titawuchubeka tinikete kukhetsa, kwehlukahlukana kanye nekuphumelela kubantfwana baseScotland.
Il faut bien le faire.
John Edwards, usihlalo we Scottish Private Schools Council
