Luhlelo lwelukhetfo lwa-Trump e-West Virginia kanye neluhlelo lwe-YouTube
Umengameli Donald Trump utawubamba umhlangano welicembu lelitsite, lomhlangano wekucala utawuba kusihlwa eWheeling, eWest Virginia.
Nguye lotawube ahambe emhlanganweni lokhetsekile welicembu ngeliviki lelitako, lapho atawube futsi eme etindzaweni letimbalwa, kufaka ekhatsi i-Tennessee ne-Mississippi.
Njengobe sekubekelwe eceleni kuvotelwa kwakhe, Trump utimisele kutfola bufakazi bemalunga labatawukhetfwa kulomkhetfo wetikhatsi letisemkhatsini, ngobe ema-Republicans asengotini yekulahlekelwa ligunya lawo eNkantolo leNkhulu nakwenteka kuvotelwa kwabo nga-November.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi sekuvakasha kwaTrump eWest Virginia, futsi ungasibukela njani sicwayiso sakhe ku-internet?
Umhlangano waTrump eWheeling, eWest Virginia, utawucala kusihlwa nga-19:00 ebusuku nge-East Coast Time, ngeMgcibelo, September 29, 2018.
Ungakhona kubukela umhlangano wa Trump eWest Virginia ku-internet, lapha ngentasi, nge-YouTube.
Ngalesikhatsi sekusolwa kwaBrett Kavanaugh, lobekabekwa licala leligcugcutela lelicala lekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi, licala le-Senate lekuvota ngekucinisekisa kutsi abe nguSomajaji belingahle limiswe kuze kube liviki linye, ngesikhatsi i-FBI isolo iphenya ngaletinsolo.
Kodvwa umgomo lomkhulu walemibutsano yaTrump kutsi usite i-Republican ibe ncono njengobe itfola kukhetfwa lokumatima ngaNovember.
Ngekusho kwaMengameli Trump, letinkhulumo letisihlanu letitawubanjwa kuleliviki lelitako, titawugcizelela kubaluleka kwekucedza emandla ebasebenti kanye nebasekeli bema-Republican labafuna kuvikela nekukhulisa emandla abo ase-Senate kanye nase-Senate.
"Kuphatsa iCongress kubaluleke kakhulu eluhlelweni lwaMengameli kutsi utawuhamba aye etiveni letinyenti ngalokunekwenteka kantsi sikhatsi semkhankhaso sesisondzele", kusho sikhulumi semkhankhaso waTrump lesingatiwa.
Lomhlangano utawubanjelwa eWesbanco Stadium eWheeling, futsi emalunga lasembili e-Ohio nasePennsylvania atawugubudzela lomhlangano, ngekusho kwe-West Virginia Metro News.
Lomhlangano weMgcibelo utawuba wekucala waTrump kuvakashela eNshonalanga neVirginia kulenyanga, lapho ancobe khona nga-2016 ngemaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 etincumeni tepolitiki.
Trump ufuna kusita Patrick Morrissey, ummeleli we West Virginia weRiphabhulikhi, kepha usephansi kakhulu eluhlwini lwekukhetfwa.
"Kungaba kubi kuMorrissey kutsi Mengameli afike atame kumenta atsandvwe", kusho Simon Haeder, umfundzi wetembusave waseNyuvesi yase West Virginia, ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Licembu laseMelika litawulwa ngeLisontfo kute liphephe kugcina litsemba lemidlalo yalo yekuhlangana
Ngemuva kwekubamba imidlalo lemitsatfu, leyodvwa ngeMgcibelo ntsambama, lomdlalo lobutsatfu longahlanganisi kanye, bekungaba nguloko lebekudzingeka kulomncintiswano we-Ryder Cup.
Imphumelelo ngulesinye sizatfu lesisunguliwe semidlalo lesentiwa ngulabadlali, futsi loku kwenteka kakhulu emidlalweni lenjengalena.
Batawutsi impumelelo yabo itfolakala kuphi?
"Bebangembili ngemalengiso ngaletitfupha, nyalo sekunemalengiso lamane, ngako-ke, ngicabanga kutsi nyalo inhlanhla isiseceleni kwetfu", kusho Jordan Spieth ngesikhatsi asuka emncintiswaneni walomuhla.
I-Europe, vele, inelitsemba, ngemaphuzu lamane embili, ngetulu kwemaphuzu lalishumi nakubili.
EmaMelika, njengobe Spieth asho, atibona anemoya lomncane, futsi angatsandza kakhulu tintfo letinyenti, lokufaka ekhatsi indlela Spieth naJustin Thomas labadlala ngayo lilanga lonkhe, futsi ngamunye wabo utfole emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulabane.
Spieth ubeke indlela lenkhulu yekuphambuka futsi uhola ngekwenta kwakhe.
Emavoti etincoco aya ngekukhula njengobe bekaya endzaweni yesigodzi, futsi wafaka phansi livoti lelimcoka lekuvikela tonkhe tinhla letine temdlalo ngemuva kwekutsi yena naThomas bebehluliwe ngemamaki lamabili ngemuva kwemidlalo lemibili.
Lijazi lakhe lelakwenta kutsi lelive lincobe emidlalweni yabo, leyatfolwa emgodzini wesi-15 weligiji, labhaliswa ngetinhlavu temsindvo, letihle tichaza kutsi usakholelwa ekutseni licembu laseMelika lisengakawinwa.
"Kufanele kutsi umuntfu adzimate abuke futsi acabangisise ngemdlalo wakhe", kusho Spieth.
Nguloko kuphela laba badlali labakhona kukwenta.
18 Emadobo ekufaka.
Emaphuzu laphakeme kunalawo lavela ku Spieth na Thomas emalangeni lamabili lendlulile, ngulawa lavela ku Francesco Molinaro na Tommy Fleetwood, indzaba lengenakuchazeka ye Ryder Cup.
Loku kuyamangalisa, kodvwa bantfu baseYurophu labatsandza kudlala badlala imidlalo lemine futsi kute labangahle badlale emaphutsa.
Ngiko nje, i-"Moliwood" bekunguye yedvwa umlingani lobekangekho esikolweni ngeMgcibelo emini, kodvwa waphindze waba khona ekutseni angayi esikolweni ngeMgcibelo ekuseni, emini emaviki onkhe, kanye nangesikhatsi sekusebenta emgconyeni wemfica ngeLesihlanu ekuseni.
Lomdlalo, nendlela emandla abo labonakala ngayo kutsi aya etulu nakubantfu labamemile, kukhombisa ngalokucacile kutsi bangemacembu ladzinga kuncoba ngeLisontfo, futsi kute lomunye umdlali lodvumile kunalona lotawusungula likilabhu laseYurophu kunekutsi kube nguFleetwood nobe Molinari, njengobe lilanga lishona eLe National Golf Course.
Indlela lencono kakhulu kutsi niyivale ngesikhatsi sinye, kodvwa ningangeni totimbili letindzawo.
Nanobe kunjalo, kusekucaleni kakhulu kutsi umuntfu angasho kutsi liCembu laseYurophu litawuncoba.
Bubba Watson na Webb Simpson bachuba kancane naSergio Garcia, liqhawe lemidlalo yesine ekuseni, lapho adlala na-Alex Noren.
Sicu kanye nemadvodza lamabili lalinganako kulemigodzi leyimfica yekucala, kwafaka umlungu kanye nemnenkhe emgodzini longaphumi.
Kodvwa ngeLisontfo, kute umuntfu longakusita uphume kulenkhungu yakho.
Letinombolo letine kanye nemidlalo yesine iyajabulisa kakhulu kuyibukela edvute, ngoba kuhlangana kwalabantfu labatsintsekako, teluleko tabo, loko labangafuni kukusho, kanye nendlela indlela umdlalo longagucuka ngayo ngekushesha.
I-Europe seyibente kancono kakhulu njenglicembu, futsi seyinemehluko lomkhulu ngemdlalo wekugcina, kodvwa lemidlalo lemine ikhombisa kutsi licembu laseMelika linemoya wekulwa labanye lebebangawetsembi, ikakhulukati emaMelika.
Emave aseYurophu anebudlelwane lobuhle be-10-6 ngelilanga lekugcina lemncintiswano we-Ryder Cup
I-Europe itawuba nemaphuzu lamakhulu ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwemdlalo welicembu lesihlanu newesitsatfu ngeMgcibelo, i-Europe itawube inemaphuzu lalishumi naku-6 ngemalengiso i-United States.
Lichembu lelikhulu le-Eton, Tommy Fleetwood naFrancesco Molinari, bahola kuhlaselwa ngemasheke lamabili, tiger Woods, lobekacedza kulwa, futsi atfola ticatfulo letine enkundleni ye-Le Golf National.
Licembu laseYurophu, laThomas Bjorn, lelifuna kubuyisa umklomelo lelahluliwe esigangeni saseHazeltine eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, liwine likomidi laseMelika ngelibhola letinyawo letintsatfu, 3-1.
Ema-United States abeka tandla kakhulu ekuchudzelaneni, futsi ancoba imidlalo lemibili, kodvwa akazange akwati kucedza lomncintiswano.
Licembu laJim Furyks belidzinga emaphuzu lasiphohlongo emidlalweni lelishumi nakubili leyehlukene ngeLisontfo kute likwati kuchubeka nalomncintiswano.
Fleetwood, wekucala we-Europe lotfole ticoco letine ngekulandzelana, yena na Molinari, labacedze liholide lelihle, batona ticoco letine ngekulandzelana emidlalweni yabo yekucala lemine emlandvweni we-Ryder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekuncoba bo-Woods naPatrick Reed emdlalweni we-quadruple, babonisa lizinga lelihle lekubambisana, bancoba bo-Woods kanye nelicembu laseMelika, Bryson Dechambeau, 5-4.
Woods, lowadlala imidlalo lemibili ngeMgcibelo, wakhombisa likhono lakhe lelikhulu ngetikhatsi letitsite, kepha nyalo sewulahlekelwe ngemidlalo lengu-19 kuleyo lengu-29 yemidlalo yakhe yema-quarter-final, kantsi sewulahlekelwe ngemidlalo lemitsatfu lelandzelanako.
Justin Rose, lobekalahliwe emdlalweni welibhola letinyawo ekuseni, wabuya wahlangana naHenriks Stenson, umngani wakhe emdlalweni welibhola letinyawo, futsi bancoba Dustin Johnson naBrooks Koepka labashaya indzima yekucala neyesitsatfu emdlalweni welibhola letinyawo.
Kodvwa eYurophu bekungasiko konkhe lobekutawuba yinzuzo kulelolanga lelimnandzi leliseningizimu-ntshonalanga yeParis.
Bawinile emahlandla lamatsatfu emncintiswaneni lomkhulu weligilebhu, Jordan Spieth na Justin Thomas, babeke umgomo wemaMelika ngemaphuzu lamabili ngeMgcibelo.
Bahlula ngekucina boJon Rahm wase Spain na Ian Poulter ngemaganu emabhodi lamane, baphindze babuye futsi bancoba Poulter na Rory Mcllroy ngemaganu emabhilidi lamane ngemane ngemuva kwekulahlekelwa ngumdlalo wekucala.
Kuleminyaka lemibili kuphela emlandvweni we-Ryder Cup, licembu lelidlale emacembu lamane lasebentise lizinga lelisetulu ekucaleni kwemdlalo, kodvwa licembu laFuryke belidzinga kuphela kubamba lizinga lelilinganako kute liqhubeke nekuphumelela.
Ngemuva kwekucedza emalanga lamabili asele, kubonakala shengatsi liSontfo lelisontfo litawuphelelwa sikhatsi.
INorth Korea itsi kucedza tikhali kwenteka ngaphandle kwekwetsembana
INdvuna yeLitiko Letangaphandle laseNyakatfo Korea, Mnu. Kim, itfule ngeMgcibelo kutsi lokuchubeka kwekutsengiselana kutawusho kungetsembeki kweMelika, nekutsi angeke kwenteke kutsi lelitiko lekucedza tikhali talo letinebuphulamtsetfo te-nuclear, lingasebenti ngaphansi kwaletimo.
Ngesikhatsi akhuluma emhlanganweni wemnyaka we-UN General Assembly, Ri Yong Ho watsi i-North Korea itsetse "tindlela letinyenti tekukhombisa umusa" kulomnyaka lophelile, njengekuyekela kuhlola tibhamu te-nuclear kanye nemakhemikhali emisebe, kucedza indzawo yekuhlola tibhamu te-nuclear, kanye nekutsembisa kuyekela kutfutfukisa tikhali te-nuclear kanye netinhlelo te-nuclear.
"Nanobe kunjalo, asikaze sikubone kuphendvula lokukahle lokuvela e-United States", washo.
Ngaphandle kwekwetsembana neMelika kute sicinisekiso sekuphepha kwelive lakitsi futsi ngaphasi kwaleto timo, akukafaneli kutsi sicale ngekwehlisa tikhali tetfu te-nuclear.
Nanobe Ri avame kuphindzaphindza tikhalo temaNyakatfo Korea mayelana nekuphikisa kweMelika kusondzela kancane kancane ekunciphiseni tikhali te-nuclear, lapho khona iNingizimu Korea itawukhokhelwa ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi, lesimemetelo sakhe besibonakala sikhetsekile, ngobe bekangeke asho kutsi angeke ayekele ngalokuphelele kucedza tikhali te-nuclear njengobe Pyongyang yenta esikhatsini lesendlulile.
Ri uchaza ngetitatimende letihlanganyelwe ta Kim Jong Un na Donald Trump emhlanganweni wekucala emkhatsini webaholi labasebenta njengamengameli waseMelika kanye neNorth Korea, eSingapore nga June 12, lapho khona Kim wacela kusebenta nge "kususa tikhali te-nuclear eKorea" na Trump wenta setsembiso sekuvikela iNorth Korea.
I-North Korea yente imetamo yekucedza imphi yaseKorea yanga-1950-53, kodvwa i-United States itsi i-Pyongyang kufanele iyekele kubhadalisa tikhali tayo te-nuclear.
I-Washington nayo ivumelene nekucindzetelwa kutsi yehlise lizinga layo leticindzetelo tekuhwebelana ne-North Korea.
Emave aseMelika afuna kutsi kupheliswe kwehliswa kwe tikhali te-nuclear kucala , futsi akhulise lizinga lekusebentisa ema-nuclear power kute kutfutfukiswe, futsi aphikise ngisho nesimemetelo sekuphela kwemphi,  kusho Ri.
? Kuphela kwemaphupho ebantfu labangati lutfo ngatsi kutsi bantfu bemabhizinisi bangasibeka etinhloko.
Kodvwa-ke inkinga kutsi lokuchubeka nekuhweba kungasenta singetsembi.
Ri akazange akhulume ngaletinye tinhlelo tekuhlangana phakatsi kwaKim naTrump, njengoba umholi waseMelika akhulume ngako e-UN ekucaleni kwalemviki.
Esikhundleni saloko, iNdvuna ikhuluma ngemihlangano lemitsatfu leyenteka emkhatsini wa Kim na Moon Jae-in, umholi waseNingizimu Korea, etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, yatsi: ?Kube lelicembu lelibukene nekucedza tikhali te-nuclear belikadze lisuka eNingizimu Korea, hhayi eMelika, ngabe lemicimbi yekucedza tikhali te-nuclear beyingeke yentiwe.?
Noma kunjalo, inkhulumo ya Ri beyehluke kakhulu kunenkhulumo yakhe yemnyaka lophelile ngesikhatsi atjela umhlangano lomkhulu we-UN kutsi kungangaphepha kutsi kubekwe emarokhethi laphuma eNyakatfo Korea aye e-US ngemuva kwekutsi umengameli Trump abite Kim Jong Un ngekutsi ngumuntfu lofuna kutibulala.
Ngesikhatsi Trump asecwayisa i-North Korea ngemnyaka lowengcile, kulomnyaka bekahamba embili ku-UN, abonga Kim ngesibindzi sakhe sekutsatsa tinyatselo tekucedza tikhali, kepha watsi kusasele lokunyenti lokudzinga kwentiwa, nekutsi imitsetfo yekungavunyelwa kuhweba itawuchubeka isebente kuze kube ngulapho i-North Korea seyilahle tonkhe tikhali tayo te-nuclear.
NgeLesiTsatfu, Trump waveta kutsi akanaso sikhatsi lesidze lesakhetsekile, watsi: "Kungakhatsaliseki kutsi loku kutsatsa iminyaka lemibili, lemitsatfu, noma tinyanga letisihlanu - akunandzaba.
I-China ne-Russia batsi i-UNSC kufanele ibuke i-Pyongyang ngetinyatselo letitsetse.
Nanobe kunjalo, uMphatsi weLitiko Letasekhaya waseMelika Mike Pompeo, watsi: "Lokuvalwa kwekusebenta kwe-TBTB kumele kuchubeke kuze kube ngulapho kukhululwa ngalokuphelele kwe-nuclear sekuvele futsi sekuvunyiwe".
Umkhandlu weTiphephamandla teMhlaba wavumelana ngekukhulisa lizinga lekutsengiselana neNorth Korea kusukela nga-2006 ngemetamo yekucedza timali tekusebentisa tikhali te-nuclear kanye netikhali temikhali.
Pompeo wahlangana na Ri emngcwabeni we UN General Assembly, ngemuva kwaloko watsi utawuvakashela Pyongyang futsi enyangeni lelandzelako kute alungiselele lomunye umhlangano.
Pompeo sewuvakashele i-North Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kepha luhambo lwakhe lwekugcina aluzange lube yimphumelelo.
Wasuka ePyongyang ngaJulayi atjela bantfu kutsi sewutfole impumelelo, kepha ngemuva kwemahora lambalwa, iNorth Korea yamlahla ngekutsi wente "tintfo letingacabangeki".
ENingizimu Korea, i-North Korea, yetsembisa emhlanganweni wayo na-Moon Mnguni kulenyanga kutsi itawuvala tikhungo tayo tetikhali letinemisebe kanye netikhungo tato te-nuclear uma i-United States itsatsa sinyatselo lesifanele.
Watsi Kim waticinisekisa kutsi "tinyatselo tekusekela" labetifuna betitawufaka ekhatsi kucinisekisa kuvikeleka kwalelive njengoba Trump bekatsembise ngako eSingapore kanye netinyatselo tekubuyela eticunjini tebuhlobo lobuhle ne-Washington.
Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza etikolweni tabo
Sifundvo lesisha lesentiwe eHarvard University sinikete bonkhe bafundzi litfuba lelikhulu lekulala ngalokwenele, kute kuncandzwe umkhuba wekutsi bafundzi bafundze busuku bonkhe basebentisa i-caffeine.
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe luveta kutsi bantfu labafundza emanyuvesi lakhetsekile bavame kuba nelwati loluncane ngetintfo letimayelana nekuticabangela.
Charles Czeisler, longulomunye wabo, longulomunye webafundzi be-Bioenergetics, longulomunye webafundzi be-Bioenergetics, longulomunye webafundzi be-Bioenergetics, futsi lofundzako wase-Brigham and Women's Hospital, wasungula le-Bioenergetics, futsi ukholelwa kutsi ngiyo yekucala le-Bioenergetics eMelika.
Wakhombisa kutsi unesifiso sekwenta likilasi ngekwetfula inkhulumo yakhe lemayelana nemiphumela yekungalali kahle.
Ekupheleni kwalenkhulumo, kwefika intfombatana kimi yatsi: Kungani loku bakusho kimi ngisesengakatfutsi?
Watsi akekho umuntfu lowake wamfundzisa ngekubaluleka kwekulala, loku kwangimangalisa kakhulu", washo atjela iThe Telegraph.
Lesifundvo, lesitawuba kwekucala kulomnyaka, sitawuphindze sichazele bafundzi ngetindlela letibalulekile tekulala lokuncono, lokutawubasita kutsi baphumelele etifundvweni, badlale imidlalo, futsi babe nenhlalakahle.
Paul Barreira, longuphrofesa wekusebenta kwengcondvo eHarvard Medical School kanye nemcondzisi we-Harvard School of Public Health, watsi leyunivesithi yakhetsa kufundzisa bantfu ngekulala ngemuva kwekubona kutsi bafundzi bebavame kulala kakhulu ngalelo viki.
Sifundvo lesitsatsa li-awa sifaka ekhatsi umsebenti wekuhlola lokwentiwa ngekusebentisa tinhlavu tekuhlola.
Kulencenye kunelibhokisi lemfundvo lelisendlini lapho bafundzi banatsa khona emabhodlela elicoffee, emafasitelo, emabhulashi etemidlalo kanye netincwadzi kute bafundze ngemiphumela yekunatsa tjwala kanye nekukhanyiswa, kanye nekutsi imphumelelo yabo kutemidlalo ingaphatamiseka yini uma bangalali kahle, kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala sikhatsi lesidze.
Kulesinye sifundvo, bantfu labebahlolwa bebatjelwa kutsi kungalali sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa ematfuba abo ekuhlaselwa sifo senhlitiyo, sifo sekushaywa ngumoya, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Likhadi lelikhombisa indzawo yesikolo lelibhalwe ngemagama lamanyenti, litawukhutsata bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngemikhuba yabo.
Sati kutsi loku ngeke kugucule kutiphatsa kwebafundzi labangephasi kwa-100.
Kodvwa siyabona kutsi banelilungelo lekwati loko, njengobe nje nawe unalo lelilungelo lekwati kutsi kubhema kuyingoti kangakanani emphilweni yakho,' kwengeta Profesa Czeisler.
Wachubeka watsi: "Tichubekelembili tebuchwepheshe kanye nekucindzeteleka kwebafundzi kwenta kutsi kungalali kahle kube yinkinga lenkhulu".
Utsi, kutfola luhlelo lwekulala loluphelele kufanele kube "silimato" lesibalulekile bafundzi labatoba naso kute balwisane nekucindzeteleka, kutikhandza sebakhatsatekile, kanye nekucindzeteleka emoyeni - ngisho nekunciphisa umtimba, ngobe kungakhoni kulala kwenta ingcondvo idle kakhulu, lokwenta umtimba ube butsakatsaka.
Raymond So, lonemnyaka longu-19 budzala lobekasati semfundvo yetintfo letiphilako, wase-California, wasita Profesa Czeisler ekuhleleni lenkhundla, kodvwa bekangumfundzi wakhe e-Harvard ngemnyaka wakhe wekucala.
Watsi lesifundvo samvulela emehlo futsi samenta kutsi amemetele sifundvo kubo bonkhe bafundzi esikolweni.
Ucabanga kutsi kutawudzingeka kutsi bafundzi bacedze tifundvo letifanako ngaphambi kwekutsi bafundze.
Phrofesa Czeisler weluleka bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngekusebentisa ema-alamu ekubasita kutsi balale, kanye nekubavusa, bakhumbula kutsi kukhanya lokuluhlata lokukhishwa titfombe te-elekthronikhi kanye nemalayini e-LED kungaphazamisa sikhatsi semtimba futsi kwente kube matima kulala.
