I-HIV/AIDS: E-China, 14 wemaphesenti etintfo letisha letatibangela kutsi umuntfu aphatfwe yi-HIV
I-China ibike kutsi lizinga lebantfu base-China labatsi bane-HIV nobe i-AIDS likhule ngemaphesenti lalishumi nakune.
Tikhulu tetemphilo tiyasho kutsi bantfu labangetulu kwa-820 000 balelekile kulelive.
Letinye tifo letingaba ngu-40 000 tabonwa ngekota yesibili kuphela nga-2018.
Bantfu labanyenti labasandza kutfola lokugula kuhlangabetana nabo ngekwelicansi, futsi loku kuyawushintja kakhulu kuphila.
Ekucaleni, i-HIV beyisakateka ngekushesha etindzaweni letitsite eChina ngenca yekunikela ngengati lengcolile.
Ngakulolunye luhlangotsi, linani lebantfu labangenwa nguleligciwane leHIV ngekusebentisa letindlela lelisusiwe lihle lacishe laba ngu-zero, kusho bososayensi labafundzele temphilo e-China, emhlanganweni lobewubanjelwe esifundzeni saseYunnan.
Nanobe kunjalo, linani lebantfu labangenwa nguleligciwane nobe lababulawa nguleligciwane lenyuka laba ngu-100 000 umnyaka ngemnyaka.
Kutfolakala kwe HIV ngekuya ecasini kuyinkinga lenkhulu emphakatsini wema LGBT e-China.
Bantfu labatsandzana nabo basemtsetfweni e-China kusukela nga-1997, kodvwa kusenekwenteka kutsi bantfu labatsandzana nabo basengakabekwa licala.
Ngesizatfu sekutsi kunemitsetfo lecinile kulelive, lucwaningo lutsi emaphesenti langu-70 kuya ku-90 alabo labenta bundlundlulu bagcina sebashadile.
Bantfu labanyenti bayangenwa tifo ngenca yekutsi labashadile ababanaki kahle bantfwana babo.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende wase-China ucele kutsi wonkhe umuntfu atfole imitsi yekulwa ne-HIV njengencenye yeluhlelo lwakhe lwekulwa nalomkhuhlane.
