NgaLwesithathu, Mengameli waseMelika, Donald Trump, wakhuluma ngesikhangiso lesikhishwe liphephandaba laseShayina, i-Des Moines Register, lokuliphepha lelisakatwe kakhulu e-Iowa, lelasola i-China ngekutsi ifuna kungenela lukhetfo lwe-US Congress lolutakwenteka nga-November 6, 2016.
Ngekusho kwaTrump, iBeijing ifuna kungenela lukhetfo lwe-US Congress, lokwavetwa ngulabasemtsetfweni e-US ku-Reuters, bekusicalo lesisha semkhankhaso wekukhulisa lizinga le-Washington yekucindzetela i-China.
Nanobe kuliciniso kutsi bohulumende bangaphandle bakhangisa ngetintfo letitfutfukisako kute kucinisekiswe kutsi kuhwebelana kuyachubeka, iBeijing neWashington solo basemphini yekutsengiselana, njengobe loku kuletsa umtsetfo wentsengo lephakeme kumikhicito lechamuka kulelo nalelo live.
Labasebenta eChina naseMelika batsi i-dollar yaseChina lebeyivele isetjentiswe ekucaleni kwemphi yekutsengiswa, yayentelwe kutsi ihlasele ema-expat ase-US, labahamba ngetulu kwe-Iowa, lebeyifundziswa ngema-Republican laTrump.
Terry Branstad, lobekasolo angunobhala we-Iowa, longunobhala wase-China, futsi lobekahamba ngetintfo tekulima letisetjentiswa e-China, watsi i-Beijing yente umonakalo lomkhulu kubasebenti baseMelika, kubalimi kanye nasetinkampaneni.
Ku-Sunday Des Moines Register, Branstad watsi: "I-China seyicala kuhlukumeta ngekushicilela tintfo letishayisana nemtsetfo emphakatsini wetfu".
"Ngekwenta lomkhankaso wekukhangisa, hulumende wase-China usebentisa inkhululeko yekukhuluma yase-US kanye nemsakato wetfu lokhululekile ngekukhangisa nge-Des Moines Register", kusho Branstad.
Ngalesinye sikhatsi, kute ngisho nalinye liphimbo lelikhombisa kuphikisana lokutfolakala etitolo tetincwadzi letitsengiswa emigwacweni yaseBeijing, futsi kute ngisho linye liphimbo lelikhombisa kucabanga kwebantfu baseChina ngemnotfo waseChina, njengobe betindzaba basuke babhajwe libutfo le-CPC, wabhala.
Wengeta watsi lomunye wemaphephandzaba lamakhulu e-China wawugwema lomnikelo wekushicilela indzaba yakhe, kodvwa akazange asho kutsi ngumuphi.
Labasati bayabika kutsi ema-Republicans ayabacindzetela bafati labasembili kute bakhone kuvota kulomnyaka lotako, ngekusebentisa i- Kavanaugh.
Labasati bepolitiki bakhala ngekutsi kutawuba nekungevani, ikakhulukati kubomake, kulokhetho lolutako lwe-Midterm, ngenca yekutsi ema-Republican lamanyenti amemetele nekugcina umehluleli we-Supreme Court, Brett Kavanaugh, lobekafake licala lekunyetwa ngekwelicansi.
Tintfo beticocene kakhulu ngaloludzaba futsi nemaRepublican lamanyenti asakuvumile kutsi afuna kuvota.
"Akukhonakali kutsi uhambe ngaletiyingi", kusho Grant Reeher, longuphrofesa wetembusave we-Maxwell School, e-Syracuse University, ku-The Hill, ngaphambi kwendzaba leyayikhicitwe ngeMgcibelo.
Reeher wabuye wabuta kutsi ngabe kubitwa kwaJeff Flake, losekela sikhulu se-Arizona, ngemzuzu wekugcina we-FBI, bekungaba yintfo letawucalekisa labavoti labatfukutsele.
"Bafati angeke bayikhohlwe lentfo leyenteke itolo, angeke bayikhohlwe kusasa, futsi ngeke bayikhohlwe ngenyanga yeNgci", kusho Karine Jean-Pierre, umeluleki lophetse kanye nemkhulumeli welicembu lemaLiberali i-MoveOn, ngeLesihlanu, ngekusho kwebantfu labasebancane base Washington D.C.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, labaphikisako behlabela 'November is approaching!' babukisa etulu etulu emagumbini eSigungu Savelonkhe, ngesikhatsi emaRepublicans labebaphetse Sigungu Savelonkhe ancuma kuchubeka ngekukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh, nangetulu kwebufakazi baDkt. Christine Blasey Ford, ngekusho kwaMich.
"Lutsandvo nekushisekela kwebantfu labamemile kutawuba nemandla lamakhulu", kusho Stu Rothenberg, losati ngetepolitiki, ku-website yetindzaba.
Bantfu batawutsi lesikhatsi sesendlulile, futsi vele vele sesendlulile.
Kodvwa kungenteka kutsi linani labo liphakeme, ikakhulukati kubantfu labasikati labasemakhaya, kanye nakulabancane, labaseminyakeni yebudzala lengu-18 kuya ku-29, labamtsandza kakhulu Mengameli, kepha lokungakavami kutsi bavote.
Babhali betindzaba babiketela ngekuhlaselwa nangabe iRiphabhulikhi itawucinisekisa Kavanaugh, ngisho nangaphambi kwekutsi Ford amemetele kutsi bekabahlukumezile ngekwelicansi.
"Loku sekuyinkinga lenkhulu kakhulu kulicembu lemaRepublican", Michael Still, lobekalilunga lelikomidi lelive lemaRepublican, kusho yena ku-NBC News ekucaleni kweliviki leliphelile.
"Loku akusiko kutsi likomidi litawukhetsa nobe litawukhetsa nobe Kavanaugh utawuyekelwa, kodvwa yindlela laba-Republicans labenta ngayo futsi labakhombisa ngayo kutsi bayamemukela", kusho Guy Cecil, umengameli we-Priorities USA, licembu lelisita kukhetfwa kwebantfu bema-Democrats, akhuluma na-Newsweek.
Nanobe kunjalo, bantfu baseMelika babonakala behlukene ngekutsi ngubani labamkholwe, ngekubuka bufakazi lobusuka ku-Ford na-Kavanaugh, lobusekelwe kakhulu kulona wekugcina.
Kucwaninga lokusha kwe-YouGov kuveta kutsi 41% webantfu labaphendvule batsi bayakukholelwa loko lokushiwo ngu-Ford, kantsi 35% batsi bayakukholelwa loko lokushiwo ngu-Kavanaugh.
Kwengeta lapho, emaphesenti lamashumi lamatsatfu nesitsatfu alabo labaphendvula batsi bacabanga kutsi Kavanaugh bekacala emanga nobe bekacala emanga, kantsi emaphesenti lamashumi lamatsatfu kuphela labasho lokufanako ngaFord.
Ngemuva kwekushaywa kwaFlake, i-FBI nyalo iphenya ngekumangalelwa ngu-Ford kanye nalokungenani ngulomunye umfati, Deboruh Ramirez, ngekusho kwe-Guardian.
Ford wetfula bufakazi lobufakazi ecaleni leNkantolo Lenkhulu kuleliviki leliphelile, watsi Kavanaugh wamhlasela ngesikhatsi aneminyaka lengu-17 budzala, nekutsi bekanatsa tjwala.
Ramirez utsi Kavanaugh wametfwala tithico takhe telicansi embikwakhe ngesikhatsi bobabili babekhona emcimbini wekuba bafundzi e-Yale University ngemnyaka wa-1990s.
Umcambi we-Internet uhlela kuvula i-Internet lensha kute ilwe ne-Google kanye ne-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, longumsunguli we-Internet, uhlela kwakha inkapani yemathuluzi ekucwaninga kute alwe ne-Facebook, i-Amazon ne-Google.
Umsebenti wekugcina walolucembu lweteknoloji, Inrupt, yinkampani leyakha iSolid, i-open source leyentiwe ngu-Berners-Lee.
Solids ivumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse kutsi idatha yabo ibekwe kuphi nekutsi bobani labavumelekile kutsi bafinyelele kulolwati.
Kucocisana naye ngasese ne Fast Company, Berners-Lee watsi ngenhlekisa injongo ye-Inrupt "kusungula umhlaba".
"Kufanele sikwente nyalo loku", washo akhuluma ngemabhizinisi etinsangu.
"Lesi sikhatsi lesingumlandvo".
Le-app isebentisa tetheknoloji ye-Solid kuvumela bantfu kutsi bakhe ema-data store abo e-inthanethi, nobe i-POD.
Loku kufaka ekhatsi luhlu lwetintfo lotitsandzako, luhlu lwetintfo lokufanele utigcine, likhalenda, umtapo wetincwadzi, kanye naletinye tintfo takho.
Loku kufana nekutsi i-Google Drive, i-Microsoft Outlook, i-Slack kanye ne-Spotify tonkhe tiyatfolakala ku-website yinye ngesikhatsi sinye.
Lokwenta lolwati lube nguloluphelele lwekutsengiselana ngemininingwane yemuntfu kutsi ngukuphi longakwenta kuze utfole imininingwane letsite.
Lelikhasi liyichaza ngekutsi "kuhlukunyetwa kwemuntfu ngekusebentisa umniningwane".
Ngekusho kwaJohn Bruce, umcondzisi wale-Inrupt, umgomo we-Inrupt kutsi inikete ngemtfombo, tinhlelo kanye nelwati lolusebentako kusita kwenta i-Solid itfolakale kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Nyalo leligama selibitwa ngekutsi yi-Berners-Lee, Bruce, losebenta ngetindlela tekuphepha lowatsengwa yi-IBM, labanye bacambi bemathuluzi labacelwa kutsi basebente kulomsebenti, kanye nelicembu lalabantfu labatinikelako.
Kusukela kuleliviki, bahloli bethekhnoloji emhlabeni wonkhe sebakhona kwakha tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa emathulusi latfolakala ku-Inrupt.
Berners-Lee watsi yena nelicembu lakhe angeke bakhulume na Facebook kanye na Google mayelana nekutsi ngabe bangenta yini lushintjo loluphelele lolungagucula luhlelo lwabo lwebhizinisi ngalokuphindziwe.
"Singeke sicele imvume kubo".
Berners-Lee ubhale esihlokweni lesikhishwe ngoMgcibelo ku Medium kutsi Inrupt ibeke umgomo wekwakha emandla ebhizinisi kanye nemkhakha wekusebenta losita ekuvikeleni bucotfo kanye nekulunga kwalelikhasi lelisha lelakhiwe nge Solid.
Nga-1994, Berners-Lee wacala i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology, leyasenta sagucuka.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile, Berners-Lee bekangumuntfu lonemandla kakhulu ekutseni i-Internet ingatsatsi luhlangotsi.
Berners-Lee utawuchubeka abe ngumsunguli kanye nemholi we-World Wide Web Consortium, the Web Foundation of the Open Data Institute, ngisho nangesikhatsi sekusungulwa kwe-Inrupt.
"Nginelitsemba lelikhulu ngemnyaka lotako we-internet", kwengeta Berners-Lee.
