Ngekusho kweliphephandzaba iLondon Gazette, Vann wahola libutfo lakhe lemasotja langaphansi ngemhlaka 29 Inhlaba 1918, bayengca iCanal de Saint-Quentin, bangena enkhunjini lenkhulu yemanti, baphindze babhekiswe ngemabhomu kanye netibhamu.
Ngemuva kwaloko, wagijima waya lapho bekunemabhondi khona, futsi ngesibindzi wahola lomgamu, wahlasela sibhamu semasotja lebesisebenta nawo, wabulala emasotja lamatsatfu.
Umphatsi welicembu lelisebangeni leli-1 wabulawa libutfo lemaJalimane lelingakabonakali nga-October 4, 1918, lokwakuyinyanga nje ngaphambi kwekuphela kwemphi.
Michael Vann, loneminyaka lengu-72 budzala, watsi tintfo letentiwa ngugogo wakhe betiyintfo "Lengingeke ngikhone kuyenta, kodvwa lokwenta umuntfu atfobeke".
