Daley, loneminyaka lengu-24 budzala, utsi akazange acishe abone kutsi wehlukile kulabanye ngesikhatsi aya esikolweni sekusebenta.
Ku-Desert Island Discs kuRadio 4, Lauren Laverne, Daley watsi ukhuluma ngemalungelo ebantfu labatsandzanako kutsi banike labanye bantfu iminikelo.
Waphindze watsi kuba ngumtali kwakhe kwacedza sifiso sakhe sekuba ngumdlali we-Olympic.
