Kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami e-Indonesia
Lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 bafile ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla kanye nemagagasi edolobheni lasePalu, e-Indonesia, ngaLesihlanu, kusho basemagumbini etemanti, futsi kubikwa kutsi linani lalabafile litawenyuka.
Njengobe tekuchumana setiphelile, tisebenti tekuhlangabetana netinkinga tebasebenti betemphilo atizange tikhone kutfola imininingwane lesuka esigodzini sase Donggala, lesiseceleni kwePalu lesendzaweni leyashintja yaba ngu-7.5 ngeRichter.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-16 000 bashiya emakhaya abo ePalu ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa lokumatima.
Naku lokunye lokwenteka ePalu naseDonggala, esihlengeni saseSulawesi:
I-Palu iyinhloko dolobha yesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, futsi itfolakala ngaselwandle lolugudla intshonalanga yesichingi i-Sulawesi.
Bekusemnyakeni wa-40 wekwakhiwa kwalelidolobha, ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye nesikhukhula sekuvula emanti kuligadla.
Donggala yindzawo lenemicebo lehlala emakhantini, lengetulu kwemakhilomitha langu-380 ngaseningizimu ye Sulawesi.
Sisulu, lokuyindzawo yekuphatsa ngaphansi kwesifundza, inebantfu labacatjangelwe labafika ku 299.200 ngemnyaka wa 2017.
Timboni tekubamba tinhlanti kanye netekulima tiyincenye yetemnotfo esifundzeni sase Central Sulawesi, ikakhulu endzaweni leselusentseni lwelwandle iDonggala.
Ema-nickel nawo abalulekile kulesigodzi, kodvwa lamanyenti awo aseMorowali, lesesigodzini lesiseSulawesi.
Ngekusho kwe-Indonesia Meteorological Agency, ema-Palu neDonggala agcwele emagagasi lamanyenti ngekhulu leminyaka leliphelile.
Nga-1938, ngesikhatsi kufika tikhukhula, kwafa bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi kwashona emakhulu emakhaya eDonggala.
Kwatsi nga-1996 kwaba nesikhukhula lesagcwala imimango lenkhulu lesagcwala i-Western Donggala, lapho kwafa bantfu labayimfica.
I-Indonesia ihlala elubondzeni lwemlilo lolusendzaweni yasePacific, futsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kwenteka njalo.
Letentakalo letibalulekile teminyaka leyengcile tifaka ekhatsi:
2004: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwenteka ngaDecember 26 elugwini lolusentshonalanga ye-Aceh, esifundzeni saseSumatra leseNyakatfo, kwabangela tikhukhula letatsintsa emave langu-14, tabulala bantfu labangu-226 000 kulo lonkhe leLwandle lwase-Indiya, lokungetulu kwehhafu yabo lebebase-Aceh.
Nga-2005: Kushaya kwemhlaba lokunemandla lamakhulu lokwenteka ngaseningizimu ye-Sumatra ngasekupheleni kwaMarch nasekucaleni kwa-April, kwabangela kutsi kube nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwahlasela live lonkhe.
Emakhulu ebantfu ayafa esichingini sase Nias, lesingasemnceleni weSumatra.
Nga-2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokungu-6.8 ngelinani le-Richter kwagadla eningizimu yeJuva, lokuyindzawo lenkhulu lenkhulu lenemabhiliki ase-Indonesia, futsi kwabangela imvula lenkhulu leyenta kwaba nesiphepho lebesicondze ngaseningizimu, lesabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-700.
Nga-2009: Kwehla lokunemandla lokungaba ngu-7.6 esibaleni seRichter, edvute nelidolobha lasePadang, lelisenhlokodolobha yesifundza saseSumatra lesisenshonalanga.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1 100 bafa.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwaba ngu-7.5 kuloluhlelo lwaRichter, kwagadla esichingini saseMentawai, eceleni kweSumatra, futsi kwabangela tikhukhula letatingemamitha lalishumi kuphakama, tabhidlita tindzawo letinyenti, tabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-300.
2016: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela iPidie Jaya esifundzeni sase Aceh, kwaletsa umonakalo lomkhulu. Bantfu bakhumbula lokwagucuka lokukhulu lokwenteka nga-2004 ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye nemvula.
Ngalesikhatsi lesi, kute sigemegeme lesenteka, kodvwa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 babulawa ngulesichwaga lesagadla sakhashane.
2018: Kuzamazama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kuhlasela i-Indonesia, kubulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo yalesichingi.
