Track Palin, indvodzana lendzala yaSarah Palin, lobekanguMengameli wase-Alaska kanye nemlweli weMengameli, uboshiwe ngenca yekuhlaselwa.
Palin, loneminyaka lengemashumi lamabili nemfica, waseWasilla, Alaska, waboshwa ngesizatfu sekusolwa ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwasemakhaya, ngekuzama kuvimbela kutsi kungabikho kuhlukunyetwa ngekwasemakhaya, kanye nekuphikisa kuboshwa, ngekusho kwembiko we-Alaska State Police, lowakhishwa ngeMgcibelo.
Ngekusho kwemaphoyisa, Palin watsatsa lucingo lwemngani wakhe ngesikhatsi etama kubita emaphoyisa kute amemetele kutsi kukhona lobonile.
Palin uboshwe esiteshini saseMat-Su, lapho alindze khona kutsi avele enkantolo, futsi ugadziwe ngebheyili lengu-R500, ngekusho kwe-KTUU.
Uvele enkantolo ngeMgcibelo, lapho akhuluma khona ngekutsi "akahlulwa" ngesikhatsi acelwa kutsi akhiphe sitatimende lesimemetela kutsi "uyaboshwa" nobe "akahlulwa", ngekusho kwalemphikiswano.
Palin ubekwe licala lebucala lelicembu A lelimatsatfu, lokusho kutsi unganiketwa sigwebo semnyaka munye ejele kanye nemali letigidzi letingu-R25 000.
Uphindze wabekwa licala lekuba "licala B" lelibeka licala lekuvalela lilanga linye ejele kanye nekufaka imali lengu-R2 600.
Akusiko kwekugcina kutsi Palin abekwe licala.
Nga December 2017, wabekwa licala ngekuhlaselwa kwa babe wakhe, Todd Palin.
Make wakhe, Sarah Palin, wabita emaphoyisa kutsi amsite nakubikwa lokuhlasela.
Icala lebugebengu selitfoliwe eNkantolo yeMtsetfo yase-Alaska.
NgaJanuary 2016, wabekwa licala ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemndeni, ngekuvimbela kubikwa ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemndeni kanye nangekuphatsa sibhamu lesidzakisiwe mayelana nalokwenteka.
Lodzadze wakhe watsi lomuntfu lomdvuna wamjikijela ngemphama ebusweni.
Sarah Palin wahlushwa ngemacembu e-anti-war emnyaka wa-2016 ngemuva kwekufundzisa ngekuhlaselwa ngekutiphatsa kabi kwemfana wakhe ngemuva kwekusebenta kwakhe e-Iraq.
