Licala laseNew York lifuna kujeziswa ngesigwebo sentfo lesimfisha kuSayfullo Saipov, losolwa ngekuba yincenye yekuphatsa kuhlaselwa kwebantfu labasiphohlongo edolobheni laseNew York, lokuyindlela lengaketayeleki yekuhlukunyetwa lokwentiwa ngumbuso kusukela nga-1953.
Saipov, 30, kucatjangwa kutsi uqashe iloli ye-Home Depot kutsi ayoshaya bantfu lebebagibele emabhayisikili e-West Side Highway, e-Manhattan, lapho agadla khona bantfu lebebagibele emabhayisikili e-October.
Kute batfole sigwebo sentsambo, bomshushisi kumele batfole bufakazi bekutsi Saipov ubulale ngekuhlakanipha bantfu labasiphohlongo futsi walimata ngekuhlakanipha, ngekusho kwesicelo sakhe sekukhishwa kwesigwebo sentsambo, lesentiwa eNkantolo yeSigodzi lesiseNingizimu yeNew York.
Ngekuya ngekwemtsetfo wesintfu, bobabili labantfu babekwe licala lekuba nelicala lekufa.
Emasontfweni lalandzela kulwa, inkantolo lephakeme yamangalela Saipov ngemacala la-22 lafaka ekhatsi emacala lasiphohlongo ekubulala ngebudlova, lavame kusetjentiswa bashushisi kumangalela emacembu ebugebengu lahlelekile.
Lesehlakalo safaka ekhatsi "kucekwa lokuhleliwe" kwalabamangalelwa, batsi, futsi bachaza umsebenti waSapion ngekutsi "wesabekako, uyesabeka, futsi awuketsembeki".
"Kulimala lokukhulu lokwentiwa nguHabibullaevic Saipov, kuletsele emalunga emndeni kanye nebangani bakhe, bo-Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, na-Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, kuhlupheka lokukhulu", kusho lesigwebo.
