Icala lekugcina lekubulawa kwebantfu labashonile laphasiswa ngalo bekulicala lelicala laseNew York nga-1953, lelalibuke Julius na-Ethel Rosenberg, labashadwe ngemuva kwekutfolakala bente licebo lekuhlola emave ngemave e-USSR ngesikhatsi seMphi yeMshoshaphansi eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile.
