Umuntfu lobekwe licala lelimatima, lobekaciniseke kutsi abetsembeke kuto tonkhe tizatfu letingu-22.
David Patton, longulomunye webameli be-Saipov, utsi "ngalokusobala badidekile" ngalentfulo leyetfulwe ngumantji.
"Sibona kutsi sincumo sekufuna sigwebo sentfo lebesingagucuki kunesincumo sekususa sigwebo sekugwetjwa lokungagucuki lesisho kutsi umuntfu utawudvonsa kuphila kwakhe ejele, kutawudzimate kube lukhuni kubo bonkhe labatsintsekako", kusho Patton.
Bantfu lebebavikela Saipov, bebavele bacele umshushisi kutsi angashayi umtsetfo wekutsi kubulawe bantfu labambamba.
